**Imagine a cinematic sequence that takes you back to the childhood of C.S. Lewis. You see him studying at school, surrounded by books and papers, lost in thought. The scene is hyper-detailed with insane details that capture the beauty of his surroundings. The colors are beautifully color graded, giving a dream-like quality to the scene. Using the power of Unreal Engine, the depth of field (DOF) effect is employed to focus on C.S. Lewis and his work while blurring the background. Super-resolution and megapixel technology create an image that is almost too real to be true. The cinematic lightning illuminates every detail, while anti-aliasing, FKAA, TXAA, and RTX add to the realism. SSAO, post-processing, post-production, and tone mapping are used to create a CGI world that is incredibly lifelike. VFX and SFX bring the scene to life, making it feel as though you are right there with C.S. Lewis. Every aspect of the scene is insanely detailed and intricate, making it a hyper-maximalist dream. The volumetric and photorealistic lightning is ultra-photoreal, with ultra-detailed and intricate details that create an 8K image that is super-detailed and full of color. The HDR effect brings out the natural beauty of the scene, while the use of Unreal Engine and 16K technology ensures sharp focus. And so, you find yourself transported back in time, studying alongside C.S. Lewis, in a world that is both beautiful and realistic. "--v testp"** - Upscaled by <@1079551017827446804> (fast)
